&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/yifan-c/cassandra-dtest&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Test:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/yifan-c/cassandra/66/workflows/2b590ea0-2b4a-4d79-8abc-347cecded0cc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/yifan-c/cassandra/66/workflows/2b590ea0-2b4a-4d79-8abc-347cecded0cc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The dtest failures should not be related to the change. The errors can be reproduced by running the dtest against trunk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no failure from tests in&#160;&lt;tt&gt;test_cqlsh.py&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Briefly, the changes are&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fetch and print all pages iteratively. (&lt;tt&gt;cqlsh.py::Shell::print_result&lt;/tt&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Print compactly when in batch mode.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Always print header and new line at the bottom for each page if in tty mode, in order to have the same behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
